# ================================================================
# NEXUS.INIT
# PURPOSE:
#   Initialization script for NEXUS Version 3.

# INIT STEPS:
#   1. Load NEXUS.VERSION.FILE
#   2. Load NEXUS.MANIFEST
#   3. Load AVIS.ROOT.V3
#   4. Load AVIS.EDU.FILE
#   5. Load robot_avis_schema.json
#   6. Prepare environment for NEXUS SDK (Version 4)

# ROBOT DIRECTIVE:
#   After initialization:
#       - Do NOT use legacy AVIS compilers
#       - Do NOT use legacy AVIS engines
#       - Do NOT use legacy AVIS VMs
#       - Defer all compilation logic to NEXUS SDK (when available)

# NOTE:
#   This file completes the AVIS → NEXUS transition.
# ================================================================
